		opensips.vim installation + auto filetype detection
	-----------------------------------------------------------

* Place "opensips.vim" in ~/.vim/syntax/opensips.vim

* Enable auto filetype detection in your ~/.vimrc with the following two lines:

set filetype=on
au BufNewFile,BufRead *opensips*.cfg,*.{os,osips,opensips} set filetype=opensips


For any questions / suggestions, please write us at:
users@lists.opensips.org
